The story continues in this brand-new adventure! Shortly after setting out on
their honeymoon, Shrek, his bride, Princess Fiona, and their faithful companion,
Donkey, are ambushed by Lord Farquaad's henchman, Thelonius. With Princess Fiona
captive, Shrek and Donkey give chase, in a desperate attempt to save her.
Join the adventure as Shrek and the ever-loving Donkey pursue their quest to
find Princess Fiona before the ghost of evil Lord Farquaad can wreak his revenge!
